tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE photography_competition_entries (
    entry_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    contestant_name VARCHAR(50),
    photo_submission TEXT,
    judging_score INT
)

CREATE TABLE photography_competition_entries (
    contestant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    contestant_name TEXT,
    submission_url TEXT,
    submission_date DATE,
    judging_score INT
);

CREATE TABLE judging_scores (
    judge_id INT,
    contestant_id INT,
    judging_criterion TEXT,
    score INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (judge_id, contestant_id, judging_criterion)
);

CREATE TABLE photography_competition_entries (
  contestant_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  contestant_name VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(100),
  submission_date DATE,
  photo_url VARCHAR(200),
  judging_score INT
);

CREATE TABLE contest_winners (
  winner_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  contestant_id UUID,
  category_id UUID,
  winning_photo_url VARCHAR(200),
  winning_score INT
);
